<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1928-01-28T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1928-01-28T18:00:00-05:00" n="373" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d373">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">817.00/5335: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The Chairman of the American Delegation to the Sixth
                                International Conference of American States</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Hughes</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                State</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-01-28T18:00:00-05:00"><hi rend="italic">January 28,
                                        1928—6 p.m.</hi></date><lb/>[Received 7:51
                            p.m.]</dateline></opener>
                        <p>45. From White. Your 32, January 28, 3 p.m. Cuadra Pasos agrees to
                            insertion of words “or <hi rend="italic">suplente</hi>” in penultimate
                            sentence of article 2. Nicaragua informed.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
